76561197983677616,Recommended,218410,984391,"Posted: 9 August, 2013",all,chrono_cross_maniac,"This is one of my favourite tower defense games to date. Having your ""towers"" be unique characters that individually equip items and level up adds a surprising amount of depth and customization to the game. It seems so simple, but it's a huge improvement over the generic towers of most games in the tower defense genre.Also, the game does a really good job of letting players dictate how difficult they want the game to be, and provides a good number of incentives to replay levels at harder difficulties (including powerful unique items). More games need to learn from this; let players decide how they want to play!Add to that terrific targeting options for towers, fast-paced gameplay, steam workshop support, and even some nice music, and I am very impressed by this game. Highly recommended."
