76561197981356193,Recommended,218410,896850,"Posted: 6 September, 2013",all,fatcoland,"Defender's Quest is a simple turn based tower defense game.  Defenders are set up on a grid, and enemy units follow a path to the goal.  The units are well balanced and versatile, and the enemies return the favor.  You can set the pace of the battles at anytime, from a complete pause, to 4x ""get this over with"" speed.  You also have the option to control the difficulty to be as easy or as hard as you prefer.  Harder the challenge, the bigger the payoff.  Real strategy players are going to find the regular game a little too easy, but the game does offer unique challenges for the elite.  Gamers new to strategy games will find it very welcoming.  It is a game for every level of gamer, from casual beginner, to advanced tactician."
