76561197995158485,Recommended,218410,24121739,"Posted: 5 July, 2016",all,Searanox,"Defenders Quest is a well-balanced Tower Defense game that replaces static towers with RPG-element-laden characters. With six classes, skill trees and weapons and armor there's plenty of customization to be had.It is a little repetative, as the game expects you to run certain levels over a few times to gather much needed XP and money, but it doesn't overstay its welcome. It's got a story with characters I cared about, which is a hard thing to do for a TD game, and it ended before things started getting stale. A well-rounded experience! :)I would sing this game's praises in the same breath as Kingdom Rush. A gold standard to the genre."
